      "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\nAndreas:\nTabs to spaces is sloppy copy-pasting on my part.  I can fix and resubmit.\n\nThe order of operations is as intended, though I could add parentheses to clarify.  \n\nI intended the [1,MDTCOUNT] range.  I tested, and as best I can tell, there's no difference between 0 and 1 here.  0 does not cause an error, and it just does the same thing as 1: Create a non-striped remote directory.",
